summary: Code initializes a Python script "webinit.py" with various commands, then runs it and sleeps for 10 seconds before killing the process.

details.comment: Code initializes a Python script "webinit.py" with various commands, then runs it and sleeps for 10 seconds before killing the process.
details.content:
#!/bin/bash
python3 webinit.py "ls" "ls" "echo something"  "ls" "ls" "echo something" "ls" "ls" "echo something"  & sleep 10 && kill $!
